<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>BusinessSpew - The Corporate Jargon Generator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf-8,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><text x="50%" y="50%" font-size="4" fill="#fff" text-anchor="middle">%s</text></svg>') center/contain no-repeat;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -moz-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color: #ecf0f1;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .api-usage {
            background: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.9);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        pre {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 15px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-family: monospace;
            color: #00ffcc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .examples {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .example {
            background: rgba(52, 108, 189, 0.9);
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #8899a6;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>BusinessSpew 🔥</h1>
        <h2>The Corporate Jargon &amp; Business BS Generator</h2>
        <p>Generate authentic business rhetoric, from boardroom speak to technical posturing.</p>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h3>How It Works</h3>
            <p>BusinessSpew combines carefully curated vocabularies with patterned sentence structures to create content that sounds like it comes from a board meeting, quarterly earnings call, or tech conference keynote.</p>
            
            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <ul style="color: #ecf0f1;">
                <li>Multiple categories: corporate, tech, startup, AI, and more</li>
                <li>Customizable sentence/paragraph count</li>
                <li>Authentic business patterns &amp; structures</li>
                <li>JSON API for programmatic access</li>
                <li>Local testing with Rackup</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="api-usage">
            <h4>API Usage Guide</h4>
            
            <p><strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>http://localhost:3000/api</code></p>
            
            <h5>1. Basic Request</h5>
<pre>
GET /api/3/2/"Strategic Roadmap"
Accept: application/json
</pre>
            
            <h5>2. Full URL Structure</h5>
<pre>
GET /api[:sentences][:paragraphs][:title]
</pre>
            
            <h5>3. Query Parameters (optional)</h5>
            <table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 8px;">Parameter</th>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 8px;">Description</th>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 8px;">Default</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">sentences</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Number of sentences per paragraph</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">1</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">paragraphs</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Number of paragraphs</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">1</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">title</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Document title (optional)</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">"Executive Summary"</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">category</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Content category (corporate, tech, startup, ai)</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">"corporate"</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        
        <div class="examples">
            <h4>Example Responses</h4>
            
            <div class="example">
                <strong>Request:</strong>
                <pre>GET /api/3/2/"Q4 Strategy Document"</pre>
                <strong>Response:</strong>
                <pre>
{
  "timestamp": "2023-11-05T15:30:00Z",
  "request": {
    "sentences": 3,
    "paragraphs": 2,
    "title": "Q4 Strategy Document"
  },
  "result": {
    "title": "Q4 Strategy Document",
    "paragraphs": [
      "We are at DEFCON 1, so you must leverage this synergistic opportunity to optimize our value proposition.",
      
      "While leveraging synergy across multimedia paradigms, we need to disrupt traditional business models and transform our core ecosystem."
    ]
  },
  "status": "success"
}
                </pre>
            </div>
            
            <div class="example">
                <strong>Request:</strong>
                <pre>POST /spew/tech</pre>
                <strong>Response:</strong>
                <pre>
{
  "timestamp": "2023-11-05T15:31:00Z",
  "category": "tech",
  "sentence": "Containerizing our distributed microservices will enable horizontal scaling and improve system resilience.",
  "full_response": {
    "message": "Randomly generated business BS:",
    "content": "Containerizing our distributed microservices will enable horizontal scaling and improve system resilience.",
    "category": "tech",
    "hashtag": "#BusinessSpew"
  },
  "status": "success"
}
                </pre>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="api-usage">
            <h4>Postman Collection Setup</h4>
            
            <p>Paste this JSON into Postman to import the full collection:</p>
            
<pre>
{
  "info": {
    "name": "BusinessSpew API",
    "schema": "collection/v5.1.0",
    "author": "Your Name",
    "copyright": "2023 BusinessSpew"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "GET /api - Documentation",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "http://localhost:3000/api"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "GET /api/:sentences/:paragraphs/:title - Generate Spew",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "http://localhost:3000/api/3/2/%22Strategic%20Roadmap%22"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "POST /spew - Generate Single Sentence",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://localhost:3000/spew/ai"
      }
    }
  ]
}
</pre>
            
            <p class="note">Don't forget to set the <code>Accept: application/json</code> header for all requests!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container">
            <h4>Vocabulary Categories Explained</h4>
            
            <table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 8px;">Category</th>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 8px;">Use Case</th>
                        <th style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 8px;">Tone</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">corporate</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Board meetings, annual reports, investor calls</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Formal, strategic, boardroom-appropriate</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #55system; padding: 6px;">tech</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Tech specs, architecture docs, engineering meetings</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Technical, precise, domain-specific</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">startup</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Pitch decks, investor pitches, startup content</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Energetic, visionary, pitch-ready</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">ai</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">ML papers, research proposals, technical marketing</td>
                        <td style="border: 1px solid #555; padding: 6px;">Technical, research-oriented, precise</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        BusinessSpew v2.0 | Built with ❤️  in memory of Wilson A. Rogers |
